title: If the display property of an item is set to "none", it doesn't take effect in new PDF emitter
OB: When setting the display property of an item to "none" in the new PDF emitter, the item remains visible in the generated PDF document
EB: The item with display property set to "none" should not be visible in the generated PDF document
SR:
1. Open the PDF emitter application
2. Create a document
3. Set the display property of an item to "none"
4. Generate a PDF document
5. Verify that the item with display property set to "none" is not visible in the generated PDF document
